These are soooo delicious. Can be made ahead of time for convenience. Received rave reviews!

Rating: 4
Delicious. Will be making it again for a second time. It is time consuming but the sauce and rice can be made ahead to save time.

Rating: 3
This was very good and I would make it again. However, the tomato sauce was a bit sweet for my taste. Next time I would reduce the amount of vinegar and sugar added to the sauce (maybe to just 1 Tbs. of each). It is a bit time consuming to make due to the multiple steps, so plan for that if you are going to make it.